snippet.title: Belle Boomerang - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Get your boomerangs ready! Belle Boomerang will launch on Steam June 3rd! If all goes accordingly, Belle Boomerang should hit Game Jolt that same day. However, it is possible my friends over on Game Jolt will have to stick it out just a bit longer. Apologies in advance!

https://gamejolt.com/games/belle/419352
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1632170/Belle_Boomerang/
